== Create a custom application launcher in Gnome Shell ==

Create a {{Path|APP_NAME.desktop}} (APP_NAME application name) file under {{Path|/usr/share/applications}} (or {{Path|~/.local/share/applications}} or directly in {{Path|~/Desktop}}) with the following content:

{{FileBox|filename=APP_NAME.desktop|title=APP_NAME.desktop file|lang=ini|1=
[Desktop Entry]
Encoding=UTF-8
Name= APP_NAME
Exec=/PATH/TO/APP/EXECUTABLE
Icon=/PATH/TO/APP/ICON
Type=Application
Categories=APPLICATION_CATEGORY_NAME;
}}

